**When should you use $casts?**

Use it whenever a database value should behave as a specific PHP type:

date → dates (birth_date, effective_date, transaction_date)
datetime → timestamps
decimal:2 → money amounts
boolean → flags (is_active, is_admin)
array / json → JSON columns
**This lets you do:**
$event->event_date->format('F d, Y');
$event->event_date->isToday();
$event->event_date->diffForHumans();


